"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"我買咗ashes, crucible同forgotten god<br />\n原裝 = ACT 1~4<br />\nashes = ACT 5~6<br />\nCrucible = 出怪守城mode gameplay<br />\nforgotten god = act 7<br />\n<br />\nCrucible 我會話唔係必買 但係我覺得個守城mode好玩<br />\n<br />\nashes 就一定買 多好多隻boss同主線 lv上限升到100<br />\n<br />\nForgotten god 又係大型資料片 <br />\n入面又有另一個無限塔<br />\n其實我玩咗200個鐘由act 1玩都未推哂forgotten god<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119acf5f770a89091af423182a1df09aaa198823","tid":1175403,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n你講titan quest我就冇玩過<br />\n不過end game content grim dawn應該多嘢玩啲<br />\n同埋兩隻game睇落後期節奏都差好遠<br />\n如果拎grim dawn同POE比會覺得grim dawn節奏慢啲<br />\n但我玩落其實grim dawn節奏完全唔慢<br />\n就算玩死靈都係忙到PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edee0e7562fc8e05d5938dd1b8128566be696df2","tid":1175403,"uid":19183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"119acf5f770a89091af423182a1df09aaa198823","tid":1175403,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n你講titan quest我就冇玩過<br />\n不過end game content grim dawn應該多嘢玩啲<br />\n同埋兩隻game睇落後期節奏都差好遠<br />\n如果拎grim dawn同POE比會覺得grim dawn節奏慢啲<br />\n但我玩落其實grim dawn節奏完全唔慢<br />\n就算玩死靈都係忙到PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打解釋夠詳盡，加大左我買既意欲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntitan quest 10年前產物，希臘神話做背景，頭呢一個鐘可以話係一模一樣既體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左有過場動畫睇，同風格近diablo之外都無乜唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0cc7026d64ed5fd33109bfbb3558792f6adc7a","tid":1175403,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dis